714
00:36:28,519 --> 00:36:30,460
[SPEAKER_02] ima na večer u 8 balun,

715
00:36:30,460 --> 00:36:32,920
[SPEAKER_02] i on dođe s nogometa,

716
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:33,880
[SPEAKER_02] i ti njega ono,

717
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,400
[SPEAKER_02] a kako je bilo na nogomet,

718
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:37,699
[SPEAKER_02] to će ti mama napravi palač i inke,

719
00:36:37,699 --> 00:36:41,280
[SPEAKER_02] o ćeš pozva nekog prijatelja da dođe tu na čaj i to.

720
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:44,320
[SPEAKER_02] E, a takva bi bila prema sinu.

721
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,199
[SPEAKER_02] A ja sam ti muž,

722
00:36:45,199 --> 00:36:47,639
[SPEAKER_02] mene moraš volit još više od svog sina.

723
00:36:47,639 --> 00:36:48,639
[SPEAKER_02] Janjetinu.

724
00:36:48,639 --> 00:36:50,360
[SPEAKER_02] E, Janjetinu hoću, brate.

725
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:59,639
[SPEAKER_02] I, stvarno, tu se upalja taj neki kliker njoj,

726
00:36:59,639 --> 00:37:01,079
[SPEAKER_02] i stvarno je kasnije,

727
00:37:01,079 --> 00:37:03,440
[SPEAKER_02] ne bi mi žugala,

728
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,880
[SPEAKER_02] nego sam primijetija,

729
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:06,420
[SPEAKER_02] sam na njoj,

730
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:11,460
[SPEAKER_02] da je reprogramirala neki čip,

731
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:13,039
[SPEAKER_02] tu unutra,

732
00:37:13,039 --> 00:37:15,579
[SPEAKER_02] ima tu dosta čipova,

733
00:37:15,579 --> 00:37:18,780
[SPEAKER_02] nemamo sad vrimena,

734
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:20,579
[SPEAKER_02] jer mi sad zapoure,

735
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:27,300
[SPEAKER_02] ali ona se počela stvarno radovat zbog toga šta ja mogu otići od vozi biciklu,

736
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:29,199
[SPEAKER_02] a ona ne može.

737
00:37:29,199 --> 00:37:32,639
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, stvarno se radovala,

738
00:37:32,639 --> 00:37:35,840
[SPEAKER_02] jer to su sve hobi koje smo mi prije zajedno radili,

739
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:37,199
[SPEAKER_02] nismo išli na balon skupa,

740
00:37:37,199 --> 00:37:41,420
[SPEAKER_02] ali išli bi planinarit, išli bi penjati, išli bi vozi bicikle,

741
00:37:41,420 --> 00:37:43,719
[SPEAKER_02] i ja bi i dalje tija to raditi sa njom,

742
00:37:43,719 --> 00:37:44,960
[SPEAKER_02] ali jednostavno ona ne može.

743
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:47,639
[SPEAKER_02] I ja ponekad idem to raditi.

744
00:37:48,019 --> 00:37:49,719
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, raduj se zbog mene,

745
00:37:49,719 --> 00:37:51,380
[SPEAKER_02] ja se radujem zbog nje.

746
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:54,239
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, meni je drago kad moja žena ide,

747
00:37:54,239 --> 00:37:59,400
[SPEAKER_02] evo sad ide u Lourdes sa najstarijom čeri za koliko, za 20 dana.

748
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:01,159
[SPEAKER_02] Idu sedam dana u Lourdes.

749
00:38:01,159 --> 00:38:03,820
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ja sam presretan što ona može ići u Lourdes

750
00:38:03,820 --> 00:38:05,880
[SPEAKER_02] i šta sam ja ostati s ovih četvoro najmlađih

751
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:07,260
[SPEAKER_02] koji će me popiti krv.

752
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:09,619
[SPEAKER_02] Sad raće me.

753
00:38:09,619 --> 00:38:12,699
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ja smatram da sam ja privilegiran

754
00:38:12,699 --> 00:38:14,800
[SPEAKER_02] šta mogu ostati sa četvoro,

755
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:18,099
[SPEAKER_02] uzeti godišnji odmor i čuvati svojih četvoro dice.

756
00:38:18,099 --> 00:38:19,800
[SPEAKER_02] Smatram da je to privilegija.

757
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:21,940
[SPEAKER_02] Šta mogu minja pelene,

758
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:24,579
[SPEAKER_02] dok mi ovi drugi kriče i govore da su gladni.

759
00:38:24,579 --> 00:38:26,920
[SPEAKER_02] Šta je stvarno privilegija.

760
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:30,039
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, danas mi živimo u nekom svijetu

761
00:38:30,039 --> 00:38:32,480
[SPEAKER_02] da je samo da je meni fino, da je meni dobro,

762
00:38:32,639 --> 00:38:34,400
[SPEAKER_02] pa kome je lijepše nego meni.

763
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:38,760
[SPEAKER_02] To je toliko bogatstvo da su iskrivljene,

764
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:40,079
[SPEAKER_02] ono bare je napisao,

765
00:38:40,079 --> 00:38:42,280
[SPEAKER_02] iskrivljene vrijednosti,

766
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,599
[SPEAKER_02] da je kojim putem krenuti, ono.

767
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:45,340
[SPEAKER_02] Eto.

768
00:38:45,340 --> 00:38:47,300
[SPEAKER_02] I onda ljudi pitaju,

769
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:49,480
[SPEAKER_02] pa imaš li ti šta vremena za sebe?

770
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:50,679
[SPEAKER_02] Ima, ja kažem.

771
00:38:50,679 --> 00:38:52,880
[SPEAKER_02] Od 0 do 24 je svoje vrijeme za mene,

772
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:56,320
[SPEAKER_02] samo što sam ga ja odlučio pokloniti manjima od sebe.

773
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:57,900
[SPEAKER_02] I to je to.

774
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:06,219
[SPEAKER_03] Može, replika Mare,

775
00:39:06,219 --> 00:39:07,599
[SPEAKER_03] imaš li što zna dodati?

776
00:39:07,599 --> 00:39:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, evo, samo na ovu,

777
00:39:09,139 --> 00:39:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] na taj kliker o kojem je priča.

778
00:39:11,179 --> 00:39:15,900
[SPEAKER_02] To dan danas se ne zna koji je to kliker.

779
00:39:17,179 --> 00:39:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam shvatila u stvari,

780
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] promatrajući brakove oko sebe,

781
00:39:20,619 --> 00:39:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] od starijih ljudi,

782
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] recimo vršnjaka mojih roditelja,

783
00:39:24,239 --> 00:39:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] tako te ekipe,

784
00:39:25,179 --> 00:39:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam shvatila ono da oni žive nekako dvostruke živote,

785
00:39:28,659 --> 00:39:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] da svaki ima svoju televiziju,

786
00:39:30,239 --> 00:39:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] ona je serija, on nogomet,

787
00:39:32,340 --> 00:39:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] da svaki ima svoje društvo,

788
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] da svaki onako nekako živi neki svoj život unutar zajedničkog kućanstva,

789
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer djeca su već otišla.

790
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam se sablaznila,

791
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] znači ja sam shvatila da ja ako tako nastavim,

792
00:39:44,619 --> 00:39:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] da ću upravo to imat,

793
00:39:46,159 --> 00:39:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] znači svak će imat svoj život,

794
00:39:47,599 --> 00:39:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] on će imat svoj nogomet,

795
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću ne znam šta izmisliti drugo,

796
00:39:51,199 --> 00:39:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] da imam i ja sam shvatila da se ja moram mijenjati

797
00:39:55,179 --> 00:39:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko god to bilo teško,

798
00:39:57,099 --> 00:39:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] znala sam da ima smisla,

799
00:39:58,639 --> 00:40:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam tila da nakon što na dica odu,

800
00:40:00,559 --> 00:40:03,179
[SPEAKER_00] da mi opet sidemo na bicikle i da se malo provozamo,

801
00:40:03,179 --> 00:40:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] a ne da budemo stranci.

802
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] I to mi je bilo važnije nego to što se ja moram mijenjati.

803
00:40:09,199 --> 00:40:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] i tu sam nekako pogazila to

804
00:40:11,059 --> 00:40:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] i rekla sam, ok, sad ću se radovat,

805
00:40:13,039 --> 00:40:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] i sad ću se baš radovat,

806
00:40:14,719 --> 00:40:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] jer to reću, pitaću ga šta treba,

807
00:40:16,679 --> 00:40:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] kako mu je bilo ono,

808
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja to prije stvarno nisam znala.

809
00:40:19,260 --> 00:40:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to nisam jednostavno imala di vidit

810
00:40:22,179 --> 00:40:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam to naučila

811
00:40:23,739 --> 00:40:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] i to mi je bilo ono kao strano,

812
00:40:27,059 --> 00:40:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] nisam znala da to može biti uopće.

813
00:40:28,679 --> 00:40:30,780
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da smo mi kroz to,

814
00:40:30,780 --> 00:40:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] nekako ja mogu reći da sam tu baš ono rasla

815
00:40:34,900 --> 00:40:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] u svim tim našim, mora reći, svađama

816
00:40:37,039 --> 00:40:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] i svim tim nekim stvarima

817
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] koje je trebalo mijenjati,

818
00:40:39,199 --> 00:40:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] ono, mislim da je to bila ogroman blagoslov,

819
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:44,320
[SPEAKER_00] zato što imala sam čovjeka kre sebe

820
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji me može nešto drugačije reći,

821
00:40:46,739 --> 00:40:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] kako to zapravo bi trebalo možda izgledati.

822
00:40:50,139 --> 00:40:51,280
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako i on,

823
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:53,179
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi imao neke svoje stvari,

824
00:40:53,179 --> 00:40:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi isto njega upozoravala,

825
00:40:55,940 --> 00:40:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, jednostavno si tu zajedno

826
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] i ono, živiš i rasteš.

827
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:02,699
[SPEAKER_03] Bogu hvala.

828
00:41:02,699 --> 00:41:04,480
[SPEAKER_03] Imamo još vremena,

829
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:07,719
[SPEAKER_03] pa ja bih radao da neko iz publike postavi pitanje.

830
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:09,059
[SPEAKER_03] Naravno, dignite ruku

831
00:41:09,059 --> 00:41:11,679
[SPEAKER_03] i dobit ćete mikrofon.

832
00:41:15,099 --> 00:41:16,559
[SPEAKER_03] Evo, Saša ima pitanje.

833
00:41:16,559 --> 00:41:30,179
[SPEAKER_06] E, Mio i Mare,

834
00:41:30,179 --> 00:41:31,519
[SPEAKER_06] hvala vam puno na ovom sviju odnočanstvu,

835
00:41:31,519 --> 00:41:32,920
[SPEAKER_06] baš ste nas ovoga i nasmijali

836
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:33,639
[SPEAKER_06] i nadahnuli.

837
00:41:34,260 --> 00:41:35,019
[SPEAKER_06] Imam jedno pitanje.

838
00:41:35,019 --> 00:41:38,820
[SPEAKER_06] Spomenuo si Mio da si bio u ekipi

839
00:41:38,820 --> 00:41:41,199
[SPEAKER_06] u kojoj crkva se baš nije gledala onako dobro.

840
00:41:41,199 --> 00:41:43,619
[SPEAKER_06] Zanima me na koliko ste vi ljudi

841
00:41:43,619 --> 00:41:45,099
[SPEAKER_06] uticali iz te svoje ekipe

842
00:41:45,099 --> 00:41:46,699
[SPEAKER_06] i da li su ljudi,

843
00:41:46,699 --> 00:41:48,059
[SPEAKER_06] da li su mnogi,

844
00:41:48,059 --> 00:41:49,539
[SPEAKER_06] ili se sami od sebe

845
00:41:49,539 --> 00:41:50,559
[SPEAKER_06] ili s vremenom promijenili

846
00:41:50,559 --> 00:41:52,199
[SPEAKER_06] i više počeli ići u crkvu i tako.

847
00:41:52,199 --> 00:41:54,360
[SPEAKER_06] Da li ti s kojima ideš na balon,

848
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:56,239
[SPEAKER_06] da li su neki od njih sada vjernici

849
00:41:56,239 --> 00:41:58,199
[SPEAKER_06] ili kako se tu događale stvari?

850
00:41:58,199 --> 00:42:01,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ja to znam često ište pričati.

851
00:42:02,139 --> 00:42:04,579
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, na neke djeluješ direktno,

852
00:42:04,579 --> 00:42:05,719
[SPEAKER_02] na neke indirektno,

853
00:42:05,719 --> 00:42:06,860
[SPEAKER_02] na neke uopće ne,

854
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:09,840
[SPEAKER_02] ali ja se stičam kad sam se molija

855
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,480
[SPEAKER_02] tad kad sam živija u postanaru,

856
00:42:12,480 --> 00:42:13,340
[SPEAKER_02] ima sam cimera.

857
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:15,320
[SPEAKER_02] Zajedno smo plaćali,

858
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:17,139
[SPEAKER_02] to ja, moj kolega sa faksa,

859
00:42:17,139 --> 00:42:19,579
[SPEAKER_02] skupa smo plaćali stan,

860
00:42:19,579 --> 00:42:20,820
[SPEAKER_02] ima je svako svoju sobu,

861
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:22,440
[SPEAKER_02] imali smo zajedničku kuhinu.

862
00:42:22,440 --> 00:42:23,599
[SPEAKER_02] Ja kad sam se molija,

863
00:42:23,599 --> 00:42:24,199
[SPEAKER_02] ja gažem,

864
00:42:24,199 --> 00:42:26,019
[SPEAKER_02] Bože, evo, vratim,

865
00:42:26,019 --> 00:42:27,039
[SPEAKER_02] ono moje srce,

866
00:42:27,039 --> 00:42:29,519
[SPEAKER_02] napraviću za tebe šta god oćeš,

867
00:42:29,519 --> 00:42:30,460
[SPEAKER_02] ako oćeš u pope,

868
00:42:30,460 --> 00:42:31,159
[SPEAKER_02] idem u pope.

869
00:42:32,019 --> 00:42:34,260
[SPEAKER_02] I onda je taj moj cimero tišao pope.

870
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:37,460
[SPEAKER_02] I onda ja kažem,

871
00:42:37,460 --> 00:42:38,599
[SPEAKER_02] ono, kada Bog je,

872
00:42:38,599 --> 00:42:40,099
[SPEAKER_02] ono, čuva molitvu,

873
00:42:40,099 --> 00:42:40,940
[SPEAKER_02] ali falijaj sobu.

874
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,860
[SPEAKER_02] pa je spustila njemu poziva,

875
00:42:44,860 --> 00:42:45,360
[SPEAKER_02] meni,

876
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:48,699
[SPEAKER_02] to su ta,

877
00:42:48,699 --> 00:42:49,320
[SPEAKER_02] ono, on je,

878
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:50,880
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam njemu tako reći,

879
00:42:50,880 --> 00:42:51,159
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

880
00:42:51,159 --> 00:42:51,960
[SPEAKER_02] utro,

881
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,659
[SPEAKER_02] i on primijetija,

882
00:42:52,659 --> 00:42:54,440
[SPEAKER_02] s menom se nešto dogodilo,

883
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:55,619
[SPEAKER_02] onda se moja ispriča,

884
00:42:55,619 --> 00:42:56,380
[SPEAKER_02] šta se dogodilo,

885
00:42:56,380 --> 00:42:57,059
[SPEAKER_02] on počeo plaka,

886
00:42:57,059 --> 00:42:57,360
[SPEAKER_02] on kaže,

887
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,079
[SPEAKER_02] hoću ja to,

888
00:42:58,079 --> 00:43:00,000
[SPEAKER_02] pa je onda on otišao na neku duhovnu omnovu,

889
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:00,699
[SPEAKER_02] pa je doživio,

890
00:43:00,699 --> 00:43:02,239
[SPEAKER_02] ta nutarnje iskustvo,

891
00:43:02,239 --> 00:43:02,820
[SPEAKER_02] pa je,

892
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:03,300
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

893
00:43:03,300 --> 00:43:04,539
[SPEAKER_02] otkrija taj poziv,

894
00:43:04,539 --> 00:43:05,539
[SPEAKER_02] danas je svećenik.

895
00:43:07,760 --> 00:43:08,239
[SPEAKER_02] Ljudi,

896
00:43:08,239 --> 00:43:09,019
[SPEAKER_02] jednostavno,

897
00:43:09,019 --> 00:43:10,239
[SPEAKER_02] u početku,

898
00:43:10,239 --> 00:43:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

899
00:43:10,559 --> 00:43:11,920
[SPEAKER_02] hoćeš svima sve ispričati,

900
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:12,860
[SPEAKER_02] jer kada misliš sad,

901
00:43:12,860 --> 00:43:13,099
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

902
00:43:13,099 --> 00:43:14,139
[SPEAKER_02] ti se otkrija toplu vodu,

903
00:43:14,139 --> 00:43:15,340
[SPEAKER_02] i ja,

904
00:43:15,340 --> 00:43:15,800
[SPEAKER_02] u stvari,

905
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:16,760
[SPEAKER_02] meni je to bilo

906
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:17,780
[SPEAKER_02] otkriće tople vode,

907
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:18,860
[SPEAKER_02] zato šta,

908
00:43:18,860 --> 00:43:20,079
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

909
00:43:20,079 --> 00:43:23,780
[SPEAKER_02] jedino svjedočanstvo

910
00:43:23,780 --> 00:43:24,659
[SPEAKER_02] na internetu je bilo

911
00:43:24,659 --> 00:43:26,079
[SPEAKER_02] rafino izmeđugorje tada,

912
